properties.description: NFS signage has this as trail 181, tho it doesn't show on the topo map. It is a .8 mile gentle walk along the stream. However, it is right next to the road as well, so it is not quiet. It runs between a parking area and an intersect point with trail 165.
properties.name: El Nogal Nature Trail (181)
